{"tid":2346291,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公民議政平台明日如期宣佈成立 籌委反駁違《國安法》論：估算政權要我哋退到邊有咩意義？","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T10:17:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"de6b2b334be46ac2a7700daa4370043a74c43a64","tid":2346291,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:06:29.000Z","msg":"籌備逾半年近期備受質疑的公民議政平台將在明日（31日）大除夕宣佈成立。據了解，明午2時將有至少4名籌委會舉行記招公佈有關平台的路線方向、並向公眾解釋近日被質疑平台「難產」的傳聞等。<br />\n<br />\n公民議政平台最先由今年6月、在17區大會上由屯門區議員張可森、沙田區議員李志宏、荃灣區議員謝旻澤及西貢區議員張偉超提出臨時動議，要求各區討論成立公民議政平台，希望平台能展現區議員意志、奪回區議員被政權剝削的權利等。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》曾向籌委查詢，有不願具名的籌委透露，平台近期難以齊集所有籌委開會，但不願猜測部份籌委未有開會的真正原因，強調平台會議屬自願性質，籌委可因應個人意願或工作需要而出席會議，平台近日亦未有收到再有籌委要求退出的通知，「總之Officially冇少到人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/IDC7PIBGSNBEJO7JTWCRRXHNQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FIDC7PIBGSNBEJO7JTWCRRXHNQA%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=8321245b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FIDC7PIBGSNBEJO7JTWCRRXHNQA%2F&h=e27e390a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/IDC7PIBGSNBEJO7JTWCRRXHNQA/</a>"},{"pid":"61a6524b6d0af9c396f55512a19610561fa57b64","tid":2346291,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8339f5afc3e7d50ee1396aa6ae3f43e9c55e615d","tid":2346291,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1c0ae97212f7db0b33050b9b3cf234ea8c1bf0","tid":2346291,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets